  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 10th level, you gain the ability to consult with your ancestral spirits. When you do so, you cast the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.4v2H3hHb3Ph9XLNd]{Augury} or @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.cg50KpBkBdPK6vPL]{Clairvoyance} spell, without using a spell slot or material components. Rather than creating a spherical sensor, this use of @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.cg50KpBkBdPK6vPL]{Clairvoyance} invisibly summons one of your ancestral spirits to the chosen location. Wisdom is your spellcasting ability for these spells.</p>\n<p>After you cast either spell in this way, you can't use this feature again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
